  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as one of eight classes, such as <strong>Fire Mage</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/2ad3df350b5e5874aa5ae0418e99ce52.poster.avif?t=1747279240\" width=500 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/2ad3df350b5e5874aa5ae0418e99ce52.webm?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/2ad3df350b5e5874aa5ae0418e99ce52.mp4?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a pair of <strong>Stomping Boots</strong> and squish your enemies to death!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/8b9b1cfab555bcfd05c7395addf66947.poster.avif?t=1747279240\" width=500 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/8b9b1cfab555bcfd05c7395addf66947.webm?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/8b9b1cfab555bcfd05c7395addf66947.mp4?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Move statues</strong> around for some reason.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/ee313bad1744d3f127ddbc32a9f72ce4.poster.avif?t=1747279240\" width=500 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/ee313bad1744d3f127ddbc32a9f72ce4.webm?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/ee313bad1744d3f127ddbc32a9f72ce4.mp4?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Catch a <strong>Yellow Butterfly</strong> and run really fast!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/5b77a872ba834e5a8336738f64c517ab.poster.avif?t=1747279240\" width=500 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/5b77a872ba834e5a8336738f64c517ab.webm?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/5b77a872ba834e5a8336738f64c517ab.mp4?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Here are a few more things you can do in Zimmer</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot treasure chests</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sacrifice at an altar</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drink from a fountain</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break almost any object</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go shopping</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steal from a shop</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Murder</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rub a magic lamp</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mine some gold</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your armor at an anvil</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lure monsters onto traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep a deer in your pocket for emergency use</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your enemies into stone </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step on a dart trap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get hit by a dart</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step on it again, dodge the darts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up the darts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get an Amulet of Explosive Darts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the explosive darts for fun and profit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blow yourself up with your own explosion</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are in a room with three doors. Two doors lead to traps and monsters, the third door will contain a room with a treasure and three more doors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An action roguelike, heavily inspired by classic games such as nethack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Entirely procedurally generated, no two runs will be the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can ascend in less than an hour, depending on how fast you play, it could be much shorter or longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 levels, or endless mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 zones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ unique items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 starting classes with random stats and buffs/debuffs (plus a 9th secret class)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of traps and monsters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >17 song chiptune soundtrack</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique monsters and items during December and October.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as one of eight classes, such as <strong>Fire Mage</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/2ad3df350b5e5874aa5ae0418e99ce52.poster.avif?t=1747279240\" width=500 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/2ad3df350b5e5874aa5ae0418e99ce52.webm?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/2ad3df350b5e5874aa5ae0418e99ce52.mp4?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find a pair of <strong>Stomping Boots</strong> and squish your enemies to death!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/8b9b1cfab555bcfd05c7395addf66947.poster.avif?t=1747279240\" width=500 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/8b9b1cfab555bcfd05c7395addf66947.webm?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/8b9b1cfab555bcfd05c7395addf66947.mp4?t=1747279240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Move statues</strong> around for some reason.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2127660/extras/ee313bad1744d3f127ddbc32a9f72ce4