l</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Avoid traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lure monsters onto traps</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep a deer in your pocket for emergency use</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turn your enemies into stone </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step on a dart trap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get hit by a dart</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step on it again, dodge the darts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up the darts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get an Amulet of Explosive Darts</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the explosive darts for fun and profit</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blow yourself up with your own explosion</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are in a room with three doors. Two doors lead to traps and monsters, the third door will contain a room with a treasure and three more doors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An action roguelike, heavily inspired by classic games such as nethack. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Entirely procedurally generated, no two runs will be the same.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can ascend in less than an hour, depending on how fast you play, it could be much shorter or longer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100 levels, or endless mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 zones</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40+ unique items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 starting classes with random stats and buffs/debuffs (plus a 9th secret class)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 bosses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lots of traps and monsters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >17 song chiptune soundtrack</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph